{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Abu Dawud","section":{"7":{"eng-name":"Prayer (Kitab Al-Salat): Prostration while reciting the Qur'an","ara-name":"كتاب سجود القرآن"}},"section_detail":{"7":{"hadithnumber_first":1401,"hadithnumber_last":1415,"arabicnumber_first":1401,"arabicnumber_last":1415}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":1409,"arabicnumber":1409,"text":"حدثنا موسى بن اسماعيل، حدثنا وهيب، حدثنا ايوب، عن عكرمة، عن ابن عباس، قال ليس { ص } من عزايم السجود وقد رايت رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم يسجد فيها","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Muhyi Al-Din Abdul Hamid","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Sahih Bukhari (1069)"}],"reference":{"book":7,"hadith":9},"chapter":{"id":5,"ara-name":"باب السُّجُودِ فِي { ص }","eng-name":"The Prostration In Surah Sad","isFirstHadith":true}}]}